and I just gave it to her.

400
00:19:13,050 --> 00:19:15,910
You're really not afraid of
others chasing me, huh?

401
00:19:16,980 --> 00:19:18,290
I'm actually not afraid of that.

402
00:19:18,290 --> 00:19:19,950
You won't like her anyway.

403
00:19:20,940 --> 00:19:22,200
Don't you only like me?

404
00:19:23,830 --> 00:19:24,630
Not afraid, huh?

405
00:19:24,630 --> 00:19:25,240
Fine.

406
00:19:27,110 --> 00:19:28,440
Okay, okay, I'm afraid!

407
00:19:28,980 --> 00:19:29,840
Afraid of what?

408
00:19:30,630 --> 00:19:32,490
Afraid you'll like someone else.

409
00:19:35,260 --> 00:19:36,060
Alright then.

410
00:19:37,180 --> 00:19:38,460
You haven't

411
00:19:38,990 --> 00:19:40,990
really gone on dates with me lately.

412
00:19:41,150 --> 00:19:43,280
How are you planning to make it up to me?

413
00:19:43,830 --> 00:19:45,080
Make it up to you...

414
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:46,790
How about

415
00:19:47,110 --> 00:19:49,110
I treat you to lots and lots of meals?

416
00:19:49,660 --> 00:19:51,150
Just meals, and that's it?

417
00:20:02,150 --> 00:20:03,210
Isn't that enough?

418
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:07,680
No.

419
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:18,980
There're others here.

420
00:20:20,220 --> 00:20:22,500
School's over. Nobody's here.

421
00:20:32,370 --> 00:20:33,170
Forget it.

422
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:56,120
♪ All the stars surround you ♪

423
00:20:56,140 --> 00:20:57,810
